Package: FragR
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Fragmentation and Raster Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Reuben", "Surname", email = "ruebentetteh000@gmail.com")
Description: FragR provides functions for spatial analysis of vector and raster data.
    It includes tools to buffer vector features, compute fragmentation indices
    for land cover rasters, and calculate vegetation indices such as NDVI.
    The package is designed for ecological and environmental applications,
    supporting workflows in forest monitoring, land use planning, and remote sensing.
